rnier\", \"score\": 0.9671866823531836, \"rank\": 0.033926356057717454, \"text\": \"Garnier\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Garnier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Garnier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time world champion obstacle course racer made it from the ground up 110 meters (nearly 361 feet) to the second story of the tower in 18 minutes.\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC Bay Area News free wherever you are  Garnier broke the previous record held by South Africa's Thomas Van Tonder, who made it 90 meters up a rope between the Soweto Towers in Johannesburg four years ago.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 431, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 431, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999560710174823, \"rank\": 4.330543156849616e-05, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.8415797103275228, \"rank\": 0.12011096133288984, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 621, \"title\