25, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On top of record holder and two-time world champion, Garnier will get to add another title to her resume this spring:Olympic torchbearer.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Garnier\", \"score\": 0.9671866823531836, \"rank\": 0.033926356057717454, \"text\": \"Garnier\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Garnier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Garnier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will carry theOlympic torchin Marseilles in May ahead of the2024 Paris Olympics Opening Ceremony, which is set for July 26.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.7840004315282807, \"rank\": 0.24225871562293735, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\"}]}]}"